channel.title: DynamikScape Release
channel.description:
DynamikScape source...
I can't give too much info, cause most of it is in the pictures.
Source - Czar
Credits - Dynamik 75% Reforced 25%
Features: Custom GodWars
4 all new quests! Never seen in this way before.
2 New minigames.
Cleaned un necessary commands and packets.
New train
Shops have new ones that you can sell any of your items to.
Adding more information later...
Pictures: If there is any advertisement in the pictures, just ignore it. This server isn't even up
anymore, so it's not exactly "Advertising"
